text: Takeaway the Nasi Padang, rice was well cooked as it didn't get soft even consuming it only after two hours and heavily drenched in curry. However, didn't enjoyed their beef rendang as they were full of tendon but I guessed there would be others who like it this way.
The Curry Puff (Potato & Sardine) was delicious, well seasoning. The Lopes was nicely cooked. Value for money.
The potato Epok epok is so good. Mee Rebus is okay.
